============
 BUGTRACKER 
============
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

various bug tracker support, define a bugtracker for the channel with bugtracker-set

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *bug-autoshow*

    :description: toggle automatic retrieval of bug information

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bug-autoshow
        <output> no bugtracker configured


2) *bug-close*

    :description: close a bug

    :permissions: OPER .. BUGS

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bug-close 42 fixed Typo on line 23
        <output> no bugtracker configured


3) *bug-comments*

    :description: show all comments on a bug

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bug-comments 42
        <output> no bugtracker configured


4) *bug-list*

    :description: list all open bugs

    :permissions: USER .. BUGS

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bug-list
        <output> no bugtracker configured


5) *bug-show (bug)*

    :description: show a bug

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bug-show 42
        <output> no bugtracker configured


6) *bugtracker-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bugtracker-cfg
        <output> options: sep=".." .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


7) *bugtracker-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bugtracker-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


8) *bugtracker-info*
9) *bugtracker-set*

    :description: set a bugtracker for the channel

    :permissions: BUGSOPER .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bugtracker-set googlcode http://code.google.com/p/gozerbot
        <output> error: unknown bugtracker type, supported: googlecode,
        <output>  bugzilla, trac, flyspray, mantis


